## Key Discovery: Economy Collapse in Second Half
- max_steps = 10000 (tournament), not 5000
- Aggressive 4a 10k = 2.06 (vs 3.87 at 5k) — economy collapses in steps 5000-10000
- Average junctions in second half drops to ~0.25 (from 3.87 in first half)
- This is the #1 optimization target: sustain economy for full 10000 steps

## Key Discovery: num_agents Bug is BENEFICIAL
- The bug (num_agents=total instead of per-team) makes budgets more aggressive
- More aggressive = more aligners = higher score in early game
- But causes economy collapse because zero miners

## Key Discovery: Different Seeds = Different Bottleneck
- Silicon bottleneck on default seed
- Oxygen bottleneck on seed 42
- Need adaptive resource management, not fixed bias

